runner class - cucumber options in runner class
features - to run the feature file we provide a path to its repository
glue - the path of step definitions package
dryRun - if we set it to true, it stops actual execution and scans all the steps quickly and provide us
missing step definitions
monochrome - to remove irrelevant information from the console
plugin - pretty - to print the steps in the console to increase readability
tags - to group the scenario fro specific type of execution

//order doesn't matter but it is always good to provide the feature first and glue next